{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal for energy providers to charge more per unit for pre-paid energy",
        "additional_details": "Ensure that pre payment customers are treated fairly and that the per unit charge is no more than the equivalent unit charge for a credit meter customer.",
        "background": "Energy providers often charge higher rates per unit to customers on pre-payments energy meters. This is unacceptable as it is normally people who are on low incomes who are not permitted to change to a credit meter. Essentially these are additional costs placed upon those who can least afford them.",
